约翰·卡彭特说他“不敢相信”他看了《芭比娃娃》：“它简直超出了我的想象” https://www.nme.com/news/film/john-carpenter-says-he-cant- believe-he-watched-barbie-it-went-right-over-my-head-3513331?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=约翰卡彭特说他不敢相信他看着芭比娃娃它就在我的头顶上Elizabeth AubreyWed, 11 Oct 2023 20:57:36 +0000 Film NewsNewsBarbie https://www.nme.com/?p=3513331 <p><img width="2000" height="1271" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="约翰·卡彭特" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我不知道艾伦是谁”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/john-carpenter-says-he-cant-believe-he-watched-barbie-it-went-right-over-my-head-3513331">约翰·卡彭特 (John Carpenter) 表示，他“不敢相信”自己观看了《芭比娃娃》：“它简直超出了我的想象”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1271" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="约翰·卡彭特" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/John-Carpenter-on-Barbie-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>传奇导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-carpenter">约翰·卡彭特</a>表示，今年夏天看完<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/barbie">芭比娃娃</a></em>电影后，他仍然感到震惊。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">《芭比娃娃》评论：格蕾塔·葛韦格的成人玩具故事非常有趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位<em>万圣节</em>导演向<em><a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/tv/story/2023-10-10/john-carpenter-suburban-screams" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">《洛杉矶时报》</a></em>透露了观看这部电影的情况，称格蕾塔·葛韦格这部破纪录电影的某些部分“简直超出了我的想象”。</p><p>他接着说，他是在家里而不是在电影院看这部电影的，他喜欢玛格特·罗比的表演，认为它“非常棒”。</p><p>他告诉该刊物：“我看了<em>芭比娃娃</em>。我不敢相信我看到了<em>芭比娃娃</em>。只是这不是我这一代人。我和芭比娃娃没有任何关系。我不知道艾伦是谁。我的意思是，我可以总结一下。她说，“我没有阴道，”最后，“我要去妇科医生那里！”这就是我心目中的电影。”</p><p>卡彭特补充道：“我的意思是，那里有一个父权制的生意，但我错过了整件事。就在我头顶上。但我认为她很棒，玛格特·罗比。” </p><figure id="attachment_3355990" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3355990" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3355990" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Margot-Robbie-is-Barbie-.jpg" alt="玛格特·罗比饰演“芭比娃娃”" width="2000" height="1275" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Margot-Robbie-is-Barbie-.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Margot-Robbie-is-Barbie--400x255.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Margot-Robbie-is-Barbie--800x510.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Margot-Robbie-is-Barbie--696x444.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Margot-Robbie-is-Barbie--1392x887.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Margot-Robbie-is-Barbie--1068x681.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3355990" class="wp-caption-text"> 《芭比娃娃》中的玛格特·罗比。图片来源：华纳兄弟</figcaption></figure><p><em>《芭比娃娃》</em>已成为迄今为止全球年度票房最高的电影，也是有史以来票房最高的女导演电影。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">四星评论</a>中写道：“接下来是一部细致入微、玫瑰色的喜剧冒险片，配以由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzo">Lizzo</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>主演的令人惊叹的流行配乐，不知怎的，它不辜负巨大的炒作。借用 Ken 最酷的夹克（在长长的阵容中）的双关语，<em>芭比</em>不仅仅是‘足够’。”</p><p>在其他消息中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/margot-robbie-and-ryan-gosling-are-reuniting-for-a-new-film-3513283"><em>芭比</em>明星玛格特·罗比和瑞恩·高斯林将在一部新电影中重聚。</a></p><p>据<a href="https://www.gamesradar.com/oceans-11-prequel-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-saltburn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Games Radar</em></a>报道，两人将合作制作<em>《十一</em>罗汉》前传，由罗比的制作公司 LuckyChap Entertainment 执导。</p><p>关于该项目的细节知之甚少，但它是由杰伊·罗奇执导的，他也执导过<em>《王牌大贱谍》</em> 。据说故事背景是20世纪60年代的欧洲。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/john-carpenter-says-he-cant-believe-he-watched-barbie-it-went-right-over-my-head-3513331">约翰·卡彭特 (John Carpenter) 表示，他“不敢相信”自己观看了《芭比娃娃》：“它简直超出了我的想象”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 《你的艺术是谋杀》的新主唱分享了加入乐队以来的第一条信息https://www.nme.com/news/music/thy-art-is-murders-new-vocalist-shares-first-message-since-joining-band-3513328?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=thy-art-是谋杀新歌手分享自加入乐队以来的第一条消息Alex RigottiWed, 11 Oct 2023 20:54:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3513328 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克里斯·麦克马洪 (Chris McMahon) 于 2015 年在舞台上现场表演《你的艺术就是谋杀》" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于“性格和判断力的崩溃”，澳大利亚死亡金属乐队与他们的前主唱分道扬镳</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thy-art-is-murders-new-vocalist-shares-first-message-since-joining-band-3513328">《Thy Art Is Murder》的新主唱分享了自加入乐队以来的第一条信息，该消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克里斯·麦克马洪 (Chris McMahon) 于 2015 年在舞台上现场表演《你的艺术就是谋杀》" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/artists/thy-art-is-murder">Thy Art Is Murder</a>分享了他们的新歌手与前主唱 Chris &#39;CJ&#39; McMahon 分手后的第一条信息。</p><p>去年九月，乐队在专辑《Godlike》发行一周后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thy-art-is-murder-replace-frontman-on-new-album-due-to-a-breakdown-in-his-character-and-judgement-3503716">宣布与麦克马洪断绝关系</a>。 《你的艺术就是谋杀》在一份声明中称“他的性格和判断力崩溃了”。这支澳大利亚死亡核心乐队还表示，他们已经重新录制了这张专辑，以取代麦克马洪的声音。</p><p>麦克马洪最近因<a href="https://loudwire.com/cj-mcmahon-comments-dismissal-from-thy-art-is-murder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">发表反跨性别言论而</a>受到批评，并在该组织的频道上道歉。乐队还声称麦克马洪威胁“如果我们不屈服于[麦克马洪]持有的各种意识形态，就会从内部摧毁你的艺术就是谋杀”。</p><p>在 10 月 4 日发布到社交媒体的视频中，乐队介绍了泰勒·米勒 (Tyler Miller) 作为他们的新主唱。米勒也是 Aversions Crown 的主唱。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cx_FiOYtofG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></d